<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.2">
<l>nīntun tuyarpiṟavi yuṭpaṭamaṟ ṟevvevaiyu</l>
<l>nīntun tuyarillā vīṭu mutalām</l>
<l>pūntaṇ puṉalpoykai yāṉai yiṭarkaṭinta</l>
<l>pūntaṇ ṭuḻāyeṉ ṟaṉināya kaṉpuṇarppē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the root of liberation that is without misery to be swum,</l>
<l>all other things, including birth that is a misery to be swum,</l>
<l>the union with my solitary master with cool Tulsi in bloom</l>
<l>who chased away the affliction of the elephant in the flowering, cool, flooding pond.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
